#

Spicy Honey Garlic Chicken with Roasted Brussels Sprouts and Sweet Potatoes

$15.99
600 kcal
Difficulty: 60%

Allergens:

SoyHoney

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeDairy-FreeHigh-Protein

Tags:

ChickenRoasted VegetablesSpicyHealthy

Description

A delightful balance of sweetness and heat, this dish features tender chicken glazed with a spicy honey garlic sauce, paired with roasted Brussels sprouts and sweet potatoes for a wholesome meal.

Ingredients

  • Chicken Thighs: 4 pieces
  • Honey: 1/4 cup
  • Soy Sauce: 2 tablespoons
  • Garlic: 4 cloves, minced
  • Red Pepper Flakes: 1 teaspoon
  • Brussels Sprouts: 2 cups, halved
  • Sweet Potatoes: 2 medium, cubed
  • Olive Oil: 3 tablespoons
  • Salt: to taste
  • Pepper: to taste
